Usage: read_sai [-help] [<name>] [-partial] [-reduce_by_flexfiller]
                [-rule_only]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
<name>                                 # specify the sai file name
                                       # (string, optional)
-partial                               # Design has been loaded using
                                       # restoreDesign (bool, optional)
-reduce_by_flexfiller                  # specify the flexfiller whether is used
                                       # (bool, optional)
-rule_only                             # only import rule in sai file
                                       # (bool, optional)